Value local_if (\S+)
Value neighbor_name (.+)
Value neighbor_port (.+)
Value chassis_id (.+)

Start
  ^\s*Local\s+Intf:\s*${local_if}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*System\s+Name:\s*${neighbor_name}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*Port\s+id:\s*${neighbor_port}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*Chassis\s+id:\s*${chassis_id}\s*$$ -> Record

